      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, runs, and could make a handy budget runabout, project, or parts donor depending on what you need. If you\u2019re after something affordable and straightforward from a seller who\u2019ll tell it to you straight, this one is worth a look.",
